<HEAD>Tornado Rips through Florida Homes, Killing Four, Injuring 15</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with two grafs to UPDATE injured to 18; PICKS UP 3rd</HEAD>
<TEXT>
   graf pvs, `Families were ...'; SUBS 5th graf to CORRECT spelling to
